snippet.title: BiuBiu Jungle Game Official Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
Download on the App Store: https://apple.co/2Wi44kq

BiuBiu Jungle is a puzzle game full of mysteries, secrets and witty characters. Solve the puzzles and help BiuBiu to restore the sunken islands!

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BiuBiuJungleGame/
Website: http://playplayfun.com/biubiu-jungle-game-official-page/
